title: Joseph Koo 2 Albums
description:
Joseph Koo is one of the most respected composers in Hong Kong. He has composed many themes for Chinese movies and TV series. His melodies are beautiful and captivating with an oriental flavour but his work has no appreciation in the West. I present two albums by Joseph Koo for your listening pleasure.

1. Joseph Koo Golden Hits (12 songs) 41.26 min

2. Joseph Koo Greatest TV Themes (16 songs) 45.48 min

Enjoy!
